  "text": "c) Throughput (Rating: Limited or Excellent): Due to the possibility of chain forks, POW has limited throughput [CITATION_1] . Some of the implementations and variations based on POS outperform bitcoin when it comes to throughput but POS still has its limitations. EOS is a blockchain based on the DPOS consensus mechanism, which can support millions of transactions per second [CITATION_2] . PBFT and DBFT can sustain tens of thousands of transactions [CITATION_3] . As the throughput of POA is bounded by hardware, not consensus, it has excellent throughput.",
